{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 8","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Atributi elementa za HTML su posebne reči koje se koriste unutar otvarajućeg taga elementa za kontrolisanje ponašanja tog elementa. Atribut elementa <code>src</code> u elementu <code>img</code> opisuje/određuje URL slike (mesto gde se slika nalazi).</p>\n<p>Ovde je primer elementa za <code>img</code> sa svojstvom komponente <code>src</code> koje se odnosi na logo freeCodeCamp:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/platform/universal/fcc_secondary.svg\">\n</code></pre>\n<p>Unutar postojećeg elementa <code>img</code>, dodaj atribut elementu <code>src</code> sa ovim URL:</p>\n<p><code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5dc24073f86c76b9248c6ebb","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-8"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n      <!-- TODO: Add link to cat photos -->\n      <p>Everyone loves cute cats online!</p>\n      <img>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[7,9],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da sadrži element <code>img</code>. Možda ste uklonili element <code>img</code> ili niste obavili vrednost atributa elemenata <code>src</code> sa navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('img'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element sa <code>img</code> treba da ima svojstvo elementa <code>src</code>. Možda ste propustili to svojstvo ili postoje greške u kucanju. Proverite da postoji razmak između imena elementa i imena svojstva elementa.</p>","testString":"assert.exists(document.querySelector('img')?.src);"},{"text":"<p><code>src</code> atribut <code>img</code> elementa treba da bude postavljen na <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg</code>. Možda si ostavio pogrešan URL ili postoji greška u kucanju. Velika i mala slova u URL-u su važna.</p>","testString":"assert.equal(document.querySelector('img')?.src, 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Iako ste definisali atribut elementa <code>img</code> elementa <code>src</code> za URL, savetuje se da vrednost atributa elementa uvek obavijate navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(code, /\\<img\\s+src\\s*=\\s*https:\\/\\/cdn\\.freecodecamp\\.org\\/curriculum\\/cat-photo-app\\/relaxing-cat\\.jpg/);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja funkcija za <code>img</code> mora biti zatvorena sa <code>></code> ili <code>/></code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<img\\s+src\\s*=\\s*(\"|')https:\\/\\/cdn\\.freecodecamp\\.org\\/curriculum\\/cat-photo-app\\/relaxing-cat\\.jpg\\1\\s*\\/?>/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/#workshop-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-8","certification":"responsive-web-design-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","chapter":"html","module":"basic-html","block":"workshop-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-9","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cat-photo-app/step-7","id":"5dc24073f86c76b9248c6ebb","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/wor